{"tid":596162,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[好多圖] 廣島蠔雞肉炊飯 & 廣島美食遊記","createTime":"2018-03-17T11:03:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-21T22:16:16.000Z","uid":106919,"like":28,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c48636c86557a3339f40d1870f0a82f16b4c746d","tid":596162,"uid":106919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T11:03:51.000Z","msg":"就快復活節，香港人又係時候「返鄉下」 - 不是喜茶，是お茶；不是水煮魚，是和牛壽喜燒；不是按腳俾小費，是回酒店前一定要行行lawson/family mart再回去貼休足時間。所以話，香港人，口體可以很誠實。但假期不多，唯有自己下廚，找我的隨意門：<br />\n <br />\n<strong>廣島滋味 &ndash; 廣島蠔雞肉炊飯</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/17/182156_11e4595d0978d67d8f853b001c95d7d2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F17%2F182156_11e4595d0978d67d8f853b001c95d7d2.png&h=018b462e&s={SIZE}\" />   材料：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/17/182310_8dfdc04364fa92013643a5bba53be03c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F17%2F182310_8dfdc04364fa92013643a5bba53be03c.png&h=dfdaccb5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/17/183433_82257f9380d2306f1acd639ffd5d895b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F17%2F183433_82257f9380d2306f1acd639ffd5d895b.png&h=7bd7ff65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/17/184352_b4482a84234dd58d9a3b78eb7e7dc6b0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F17%2F184352_b4482a84234dd58d9a3b78eb7e7dc6b0.png&h=2d6bb3b1&s={SIZE}\" />  詳細食譜請到wordpress/ Facebook。<br />\n<br />\n蠔的鮮味是整鍋飯的主角，加上了菇類、雞肉和腐皮，令簡單的飯變得豐富～是回家三十分鐘就能做好的方便飯。"},{"pid":"f9124d7843452a0f75aff3da2b9c20c22d80cdfb","tid":596162,"uid":106919,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T11:04:38.000Z","msg":" --------------------------<br />\n<br />\n 我在二零一七年十二月時去了一趟廣島，這是一個非常美麗而具有歷史負重的地方。在原爆一役中，失去的人命，燒焦的土地，破碎的許多物事，就只剩下一個鐘頂的建築。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/17/183222_933064af5fbb5526be4e18c74d0a0892.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F17%2F183222_933064af5fbb5526be4e18c74d0a0892.png&h=cae01199&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n那天的天氣晴朗得要緊，空氣的清新仍然在我腦中盤旋 - 我不能想像爆炸時那種可怕，籠罩著整個國家。戰爭是數字，發生在甚麼年、死傷者有幾多、威力有多少級，但背後盛載的，卻是多少故事。只能珍惜當下的美好。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/17/183549_b351646b4b443f199afb94068b301834.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F17%2F183549_b351646b4b443f199afb94068b301834.png&h=8d6f472a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  廣島美食方面：<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/17/183506_10514702e05709c9b79c11e0e9fb256e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F17%2F183506_10514702e05709c9b79c11e0e9fb256e.png&h=01a04eda&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/17/183508_111d0394096164df1f2fdfba14827a1f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F17%2F183508_111d0394096164df1f2fdfba14827a1f.png&h=f39ce7d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 在長田屋對面的小酒館，食海鮮tapas。 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/17/183707_ed5f259d5bedc94b2c8756bddc8cfe73.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F17%2F183707_ed5f259d5bedc94b2c8756bddc8cfe73.png&h=40886a35&s={SIZE}\" /> 當然不能錯過長田屋的廣島燒。有鐵板烘著，熱烘烘的，加上那些蔥和燒汁^_^ <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/17/183623_a619fbaa43d026a4dbfc1585d934fe2b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F17%2F183623_a619fbaa43d026a4dbfc1585d934fe2b.png&h=2371f517&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n同一個晚上，再去GRAM食伯爵茶pancake。這伴著輕柔的伯爵茶味和原味忌廉、雲呢拿雪糕和煮過的蘋果。日本的忌廉是令人上癮的！北海道六花亭的泡芙更是天堂與邪惡交替。返唔到轉頭食香港甜點的其中一個原因。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/17/183104_3083e4eaed6b16855c93b4a3b430cf31.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F17%2F183104_3083e4eaed6b16855c93b4a3b430cf31.png&h=728171ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在宮島的小鹿比較乖（沒有奈良的鹿仙貝影響？）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/17/185938_e54dcad6f051d69a7c96909590f0e3f2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F17%2F185938_e54dcad6f051d69a7c96909590f0e3f2.png&h=3b72a16d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/17/184546_56cfe9480e972b4c6e45046faaa5d7b5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F17%2F184546_56cfe9480e972b4c6e45046faaa5d7b5.png&h=a84a50da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n地道的廣島蠔，有生的、烤的、做成薯餅的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/17/182944_8874a5bbb1028f006f270be69426cc32.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F17%2F182944_8874a5bbb1028f006f270be69426cc32.png&h=3a6944eb&s={SIZE}\" />是竹輪串，超好食。是第一的街頭小食（我最喜歡是枝豆味，混有枝豆好好咬口XD）但我最愛的一定是長洲甘永泰魚蛋。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/17/182920_4dfd6dc2126da545d7f7fb7648d415c1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F17%2F182920_4dfd6dc2126da545d7f7fb7648d415c1.png&h=592a7a13&s={SIZE}\" />還有日本人很愛的咖啡（和一系列咖啡甜品）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/17/183025_d3e6a405336fb75201a29ec34c0659e0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F17%2F183025_d3e6a405336fb75201a29ec34c0659e0.png&h=30df3684&s={SIZE}\" />仲有Red Rock牛肉飯。（大推前面的！）"},{"pid":"fb8e6329424f58d9a86cbda0a12a2e7af6c3c9ee","tid":596162,"uid":106919,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T11:04:54.000Z","msg":" ---------------------------<br />\n<br />\n 到底日本的情意結是從那時開始的？我也說不清。而日本能夠帶給700萬人的嚮往和快樂，已經不只是地理上的限制：東京大阪，而是米子岡山德島高松白川鄉這些可能連日本人也未去過的地方。即使是鄉間地方的一間咖啡店，畫面是一位穿著整齊筆挺的侍應，端著一杯熱騰騰的咖啡，伴的牛奶也具有相同的熱度。在悠然的爵士音樂下，你看著上升的水蒸氣，就忘掉了平時的港鐵延誤以及早餐的11蚊空氣腸仔包。可能，這就是我們的幸福吧。 "},{"pid":"4eec5fb1eeacd2f0e9d41311a753b002068b4326","tid":596162,"uid":106919,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T11:07:52.000Z","msg":"----------------------------<br />\n<br />\nWordpress:<br />\n<a href=\"http://supermarketfantasyblog.wordpress.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsupermarketfantasyblog.wordpress.com&d=HhrV9QICtMoLAXEpl4XVbTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=12cedc3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">supermarketfantasyblog.wordpress.com</a><br />\nFacebook: <br />\nsupermarketfantasy 超級市場幻想<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Supermarketfantasy-超級市場幻想-1909246362631621/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FSupermarketfantasy-%E8%B6%85%E7%B4%9A%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E5%B9%BB%E6%83%B3-1909246362631621%2F&d=HhrV9QICtMoLAXEpl4XVbTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=98169975\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Supermarketfantasy-超級市場幻想-1909246362631621/</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/smfsupermarketfantasy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fsmfsupermarketfantasy&d=HhrV9QICtMoLAXEpl4XVbTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=c774ae91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/smfsupermarketfantasy</a>"},{"pid":"84296fad050c7272e1902571f85a9654c0cc309d","tid":596162,"uid":44289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T11:10:19.000Z","msg":"嘩屌